{"tid":950328,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本外務省譴責中國黑客攻擊      強烈支持美國維護網絡秩序的決心","createTime":"2018-12-21T12:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T16:34:53.000Z","uid":39464,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b7c678d7690670b6e69c8da51eaf05099d8b5566","tid":950328,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T12:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1434511_1_L_20181221195316.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1434511_1_L_20181221195316.jpg&h=f3ee4e2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國起訴兩名中國公民，指他們入侵美國及另外11個國家的電腦系統，包括日本，日本內閣官房長官菅義偉表示，堅決譴責有關攻擊，強烈支持美國維護網絡秩序的決心。<br />\n<br />\n菅義偉說，已經確認網絡攻擊包括政府機關，屬長時間和大範圍，但他並無透露遭到攻擊的企業和團體名稱，及損失程度。<br />\n<br />\n外務省亦點名批評中國，發言人表示，包括中國在內的20國集團作為國際社會的一員，需進行負責任的應對。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1434511-20181221.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1434511-20181221.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=wDVAXzvVilOAhyVKrYBI7wEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=64a6ab71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1434511-20181221.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e3eeb6dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1434511-20181221.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"65009ffc73a11bbc4ec5a6dbe1e40a6afdc64937","tid":950328,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T12:10:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d8f5bfd364bba66e9f22fea90fdb617f96c74e7","tid":950328,"uid":213877,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"65009ffc73a11bbc4ec5a6dbe1e40a6afdc64937","tid":950328,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T12:10:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T12:17:23.000Z","msg":"中國咪有你呢類戇鳩仔囉"},{"pid":"b388161f20725